verbose_text: Next, the in vitro and in vivo experiments were conducted to evaluate the antiviral effect of gRNA-miR-HBV-gRNA ternary cassette, and showed that this ternary cassette could efficiently suppress the replication of genotype A to D HBV, including the levels of HBsAg, HBeAg and HBcAg.
